林青霞发心起愿，为抗击疫情尽自己的努力——要给最有需要的人送去最及时、最有用的物资，并将这份关爱送到祖国大陆和台港澳同胞们的手中。
Lin Qingxia vowed to do her part to fight the epidemic by sending the most timely and useful materials to those most in need and sending this care to her compatriots on the mainland and in Taiwan.
文| 王悦阳近日，林青霞的一封亲笔信，感动了无数人。
Wang Yueyang, a personal letter from Lin Qingxia, moved countless people recently.
作为中国华语影坛最具传奇色彩的演员，林青霞有过许多经典作品，诸如《窗外》《我是一片云》《金玉良缘红楼梦》《新蜀山剑侠传》《滚滚红尘》等，影响深远，粉丝众多。
As one of the most legendary actors in Chinese Chinese film industry, Lin Qingxia has many classic works, such as "I am a Cloud" "Golden Mile Red Mansion Dream" and "New Shu Mountain Swordsman" "Rolling Dust" with far-reaching influence and many fans.
尤其林青霞的美更是不可方物，因而被喜爱她的粉丝称为“东南亚第一美人”，作家琼瑶曾经这样评价过林青霞:“从来没遇到过第二个可以跟青霞媲美的女子，林青霞不光外表非常的美丽，而且也是一个心地善良的女人。
Lin Qingxia's beauty is even more inescapable, so she is called "the first beauty in Southeast Asia" by her fans. The writer Qiong Yao once remarked on Lin Qingxia: "I have never met a woman like Qingxia who is not only very beautiful in appearance but also a kind-hearted woman.
”此次亲笔写下致前线抗疫英雄的这封信，是林青霞近日来的所思所想，她希望通过自己的文字，传递一份信心，一个支持，一股力量给到所有奋战在前线的抗疫英雄，让他们知道，他们在前线并不是孤军作战，大家都是在他们身后，为他们加油打气。
This handwritten letter to the frontline anti-epidemic hero is something Lin Qingxia has been thinking about in recent days. She hopes to convey through her own words a message of confidence, support and strength to all the battle heroes who fought on the front lines that they are not alone on the front lines and that everyone is behind them, cheering them on.
近一个月来，身在香港的林青霞始终关心着全国各地疫情的发展动向，最美逆行者的义无反顾，广大医务人员的尽心尽力，越来越多的病人走向康复……每一件事都牵动着她的心。
For nearly a month, Lin Qingxia, who is in Hong Kong, has been concerned about the development of the epidemic in all parts of the country, the most beautiful inverse, the dedication of the medical staff, more and more patients to recover... everything touches her heart.
在与金圣华、贾安宜、辛丹妮等香港、大陆、台湾的三位朋友们交流的过程中，林青霞发心起愿，为抗击疫情尽自己的努力——要给最有需要的人送去最及时、最有用的物资，并将这份关爱送到祖国大陆和台港澳同胞们的手中。
In the course of exchanges with three friends from Hong Kong, mainland China and Taiwan, including Kim Sung-wah, Jia An-yi and Cindani, Lin Qingxia vowed to do her part to fight the epidemic by delivering the most timely and useful materials to those most in need and by delivering this care to her compatriots on the mainland and in Taiwan.
恰在此时，一位朋友向林青霞传来一张照片，图中，一名申请到武汉支援前线的医护人员，在防护衣后面写上“我爱林青霞”，显然她是青霞的忠实粉丝，上战场的时候，不忘让偶像“陪伴”自己。
Just then, a friend sent a photo to Lin Qingxia. In the picture, a medical worker who applied to Wuhan support front wrote "I love Lin Qingxia" on the back of the jacket.
一张小小的照片，传递出的感动与温情，令林青霞为之动容不已，或许，自己的一句话，一份祝福，就能为抗疫第一线的工作者带来无穷鼓励与信心。
A small photograph, the transmission of touched and tender feelings, so that Lin Qingxia for its moving face, perhaps, his own words, a blessing, can bring unlimited encouragement and confidence to the front-line workers against the disease.
于是，夜深人静之际，林青霞开始动笔写下心中的话，为医务工作者的勇气与爱心点赞，加油——致前线的抗疫英雄：这是一场没有硝烟的战争，这是一场没有流血的战争，这是一场史无前例的新世纪疫战。
Then, in the dead of night, Lin Qingxia began to write down his words, praise the courage and love of medical workers, cheer - to the battle against the epidemic on the frontline: a war without smoke, a war without bloodshed, an unprecedented epidemic in the new century.
你们的战袍是防弹衣，你们的头盔是口罩，你们的战场是医院。
Your war robes are flak jackets, your helmets are masks, your battlefields are hospitals.
敌人是无声无息，无色无味，防不胜防的新型冠状病毒，全世界的目光正见证你们以敬业的精神、钢铁的意志、超凡的勇气、悲悯的胸怀，巡行在医院的长廊，不分昼夜，随时应战守护他人的生命。
The enemy is a noiseless, colorless and tasteless new coronavirus, the eyes of the world are witness to you with professionalism, iron will, extraordinary courage, compassion, patrol the hospital corridors, day and night, ready to protect the lives of others.
我们知道，我们明白，我们心疼，我们流泪。
We know, we know, we love, we weep.
只想告诉你们，你们并不孤单，在大后方，有无数的人在关怀，在支持，在为你们祈祷。
Just want to tell you, you are not alone, in the rear, there are countless people caring, supporting, praying for you.
前线英勇的医护人员，我深深地敬佩你们，希望你们继续做好防护工作，保护自己，保护家人，保护同事，保护病人。
I admire you very much for your valiant medical staff. I hope you will continue to do your best to protect yourself, your families, your colleagues and your patients.
在此，谨以最虔诚的心祝福各位平平安安！健健康康！早日功成返家，与家人团聚！青霞，2020年2月23日一封书信，纸短情长。
Hereby, I wish you all peace and good health and health! Reunion with your family! Qingxia, February 23, 2020 a letter, short-term sentiment.
爽朗大气的字迹，真诚细腻的情感，朴实生动的语言，透露出林青霞最真挚的情感、关怀与祝福。
Shuang Shuang atmospheric handwriting, sincere exquisite feelings, simple and vivid language, revealed the most sincere feelings, care and blessing.
写完这封信，已是第二天的凌晨，林青霞用邮件传给了身边的好友们，不久就得到了大家热烈的响应与反馈。
After writing this letter, it is the early morning of the next day, Lin Qingxia by e-mail to friends around, soon got warm response and feedback.
著名导演赖声川看到后，将信的全文通过媒体公之于众，一时间，传播迅速，反响热烈，大家不仅赞美林青霞“人美字美”，更感动于她的一颗大爱之心。
The famous director Lai Shengchuan saw the letter through the media to the public, a time, rapid dissemination, enthusiastic response, not only praise Lin Qingxia "beauty of the word," but also moved her a great love heart.
事实上，书信只是开始。
In fact, letters are just the beginning.
在林青霞的感召下，上海的闺蜜好友贾安宜，以及大成律师事务所的张一君律师与林沙女士、王熠星先生等一起，建立了“好友群”，并已通过正规渠道筹集医疗物资，不日即将送达武汉抗疫第一线。
Inspired by Lin Qingxia, Shanghai's best friend Jia An-yi, as well as lawyer Zhang Yijun of Dacheng Law Firm, together with Ms. Lin Sha and Mr. Wang Yingxing, have established a "group of friends" and have raised medical supplies through regular channels.
之后还会有更多批的物资，会陆续送到祖国大陆和台港澳的同胞手中。
More supplies will be sent to compatriots in mainland China and Taiwan in succession.
在这批林青霞与朋友们捐赠的医疗物资上，每一个箱子上都有一幅画，那是上海的书法家王宇鸣先生的创作——一颗红红的爱心，底部仿佛一根连接内地与香港的爱心丝带，整幅画面的造型则更像一只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。
On each box, Lin Qingxia and her friends donated medical supplies, a painting by Shanghai calligrapher Mr. Wang Yuming - a red heart, with a heart-felt ribbon connecting the Mainland and Hong Kong at the bottom, and the whole image is more like a dancing butterfly.
林青霞笑着说道：“这叫开心，希望疫情尽快过去，每个家庭都开开心心！”朴素的语言却有深刻的寓意。
Lin Qingxia said with a smile: "This is called happy, hope that the epidemic situation as soon as possible, every family happy!"
值得一提的是，每一个箱子里，都有林青霞亲笔写的这封信，以此表达自己最由衷的祝福与心情。
It is worth mentioning that in each box, Lin Qingxia wrote this letter, to express their most heartfelt blessing and mood.
为了医务工作者能收到这封信，林青霞这几天认认真真地抄写了十个多小时，写干了四支笔。
In order that the medical workers can receive this letter, Lin Qingxia these days carefully transcribed more than 10 hours, wrote four pens.
一笔一画，一丝不苟，都可谓饱含深情。
One painting, meticulous, can be said to be full of affectionate.
“这是我义无反顾要去做的一件事，我感到很高兴。
"This is one thing I will do without hesitation, and I am very happy.
衷心感佩医务工作者们的努力与付出，敬祝平安！”林青霞由衷地说道。
Sincerely appreciate the efforts of medical workers and pay, I wish peace! "Lin Qingxia sincerely said.
征集令《新民周刊》现面向全国征集新冠肺炎采访对象和真实故事：如果你是参与抗击新冠肺炎疫情的医护人员或其家属，我们希望聆听你的“战疫”故事，也希望传达你的诉求。
Call for orders The New People's Weekly is now soliciting interviews and true stories from all over the country: If you are a healthcare worker or family member involved in the fight against the outbreak, we hope to hear your "epidemic" story and convey your message.
如果你是确诊、疑似患者本人或家属，我们希望了解你和家人如何“抗疫”的过程，让外界了解你的真实经历。
If you are a confirmed, suspected patient or family member, we would like to know how you and your family have responded to the epidemic and let the outside world know about your true experience.
如果你是疫情严重地区的普通市民，我们希望展现你的乐观，并倾听你所需的帮助。
If you are an ordinary citizen of a highly affected area, we hope to show your optimism and listen to the help you need.
如果你是公共服务人员或各类捐助者，我们希望看到你的“最美逆行”，记录下你的无私。
If you are a public service provider or a variety of donors, we want to see your "most beautiful retrograde" and record your selflessness.
……抗击新冠肺炎疫情，我们诚征对疫情了解的社会各界人士，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
To fight the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic, we sincerely invite all sectors of the community to understand the epidemic, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
